en_170013_0	Northern Provincial Council’s former Transport Minister B. Deniswaran has filed a petition at the Court of Appeal against his removal from the ministerial post.
en_170013_1	In the petition he had cited that the Chief Minister has no authority to make such changes in ministerial posts. Issues in ministerial posts in the NPC arose, a committee was set up by the Chief Minister to probe alleged fraud and corruptions.
en_170013_2	Thereafter, Deniswaran was removed and the Chief Minister took over the ministry.
